org.shared.parallel

Class Engine<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.shared.parallel.Engine<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the input type.

    public class Engine<T>
extends Object
    An execution engine class for pushing data through the guts of some parallel computation given as a directed, acyclic graph.
